1) copy local.php.sample to local.php

2) copy .htaccess.sample to .htaccess

3) consider putting 3rd party JavaScript and CSS in the lib folder.

4) consider putting your original JavaScript in js folder

5) consider putting 3rd-party style includes in header.php

6) consider putting your JavaScript includes in footer.php

7) see example-page.php for add_action example

8) see header.php and footer.php for do_action example

9) home.php is your homepage